## Output Format — Setup modes

**Setup team:** read `references/team-brain-schema.md` § "Upgrade flow". List people without extended fields, ask about seniority + can_substitute_for in batches of 3-5, write back preserving structure. Never overwrite or delete.

**Setup bench:** read `references/team-brain-schema.md` § "Setup bench mode". Ask for 3-5 trusted freelancers (name, role, day rate, lead time, last engaged, notes). Write `freelance-bench.md`.

## Output Format — Scenario mode

Read `references/scenarios.md`. Use the scenario diff format (baseline → change → diff → verdict → mitigations → recommendation). Don't reprint the full Resource Conflict Report.

## Output Format — Calibrate mode

Read `references/team-brain-schema.md` § "Calibrate mode". Walk through 5 questions (project / planned / actual / cause / lesson), append to `learnings.md § Capacity` per the schema. Always append, never overwrite.

